I have always loved wines of place. Over the years, I was fortunate to visit the original Kistler Vineyard on Moon Mountain with Steve Kistler several times. We will be exploring the nuances of the AVA this Saturday with two immersive tastings.

See the link in my bio or the Vinous home page for more details, including links for purchasing tickets. It’s going to be great 🤓🤓🤓😍😍😍

